ActCanada Marine Act
SubjectSept-Îles Port Authority ** LETTERS PATENT ** **AMENDMENT**
PrecisOrder approving proposed supplementary LETTERS PATENT provisions increasing the aggregate limit on the power of the SEPT-ÎLES PORT AUTHORITY to borrow money on the credit of the port authority for port purposes and adding two further borrowing limits specific to identified projects.
